#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.okular.kirigami.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"Okular is a universal document viewer developed by KDE. Okular works on "
"multiple platforms, including but not limited to Linux, Windows, Mac OS X, "
"*BSD, etc."
msgstr ""
"Okular és un visor universal de documents desenvolupat per KDE. Okular "
"funciona en múltiples plataformes, incloent-hi però sense limitar-se a "
"Linux, Windows, Mac OS X, *BSD, etc."

